    {
      "id": "book05-the-caterpillar",
      "name": "THE CATERPILLAR",
      "level": 1,
      "category": "booklet",
      "sort_order": 5,
      "sections": {
        "Page 1": "ALICE MET A BIG CATERPILLAR.\nHE SAT ON A MUSHROOM AND SMOKED.\n\"WHO ARE YOU?\" HE ASKED.",
        "Page 2": "\"I DON'T KNOW!\" SAID ALICE.\n\"I KEEP CHANGING SIZE.\nI AM NOT MYSELF TODAY.\"",
        "Page 3": "THE CATERPILLAR TOLD HER A SECRET.\n\"ONE SIDE MAKES YOU TALL.\nTHE OTHER SIDE MAKES YOU SMALL.\"\nIT WAS THE MUSHROOM!",
        "Page 4": "ALICE ATE A BIT OF MUSHROOM.\nHER NECK GREW VERY, VERY LONG!\nA BIRD CALLED HER A SERPENT.\n\"I AM NOT A SERPENT! I AM A GIRL!\""
      },
