      "id": "book08-the-queens-garden",
      "name": "THE QUEEN'S GARDEN",
      "level": 1,
      "category": "booklet",
      "sort_order": 8,
      "sections": {
        "Page 1": "ALICE FOUND A GARDEN.\nTHREE CARDS WERE PAINTING ROSES RED.\n\"WHY?\" ASKED ALICE.\n\"THE QUEEN WANTED RED ROSES.\nWE PLANTED WHITE ONES BY MISTAKE!\"",
        "Page 2": "THE QUEEN OF HEARTS MARCHED IN.\n\"OFF WITH THEIR HEADS!\" SHE SHOUTED.\nBUT ALICE HID THE CARDS.\n\"THEY ARE SAFE,\" SHE WHISPERED.",
        "Page 3": "\"LET US PLAY CROQUET!\" SAID THE QUEEN.\nTHE BALLS WERE HEDGEHOGS.\nTHE MALLETS WERE FLAMINGOS!\nNOBODY PLAYED BY THE RULES.",
        "Page 4": "THE CHESHIRE CAT APPEARED AGAIN.\nJUST HIS HEAD — FLOATING IN THE AIR!\n\"YOU CAN'T CUT OFF A HEAD\nWITH NO BODY,\" SAID ALICE."
      },
