    {
      "id": "book09-the-mock-turtle",
      "name": "THE MOCK TURTLE",
      "level": 1,
      "category": "booklet",
      "sort_order": 9,
      "sections": {
        "Page 1": "ALICE MET THE DUCHESS AGAIN.\n\"EVERYTHING HAS A MORAL!\" SHE SAID.\n\"THE MORAL IS: LOVE MAKES THE WORLD GO ROUND.\"\n\"SOMEBODY SAID IT'S MINDING YOUR OWN BUSINESS!\" SAID ALICE.",
        "Page 2": "THE QUEEN SENT ALICE TO MEET\nTHE GRYPHON AND THE MOCK TURTLE.\nTHE MOCK TURTLE WAS VERY SAD.\n\"ONCE I WAS A REAL TURTLE,\" HE CRIED.",
        "Page 3": "\"WE WENT TO SCHOOL IN THE SEA,\" HE SAID.\n\"WE LEARNED REELING AND WRITHING\nAND THE DIFFERENT BRANCHES OF ARITHMETIC:\nAMBITION, DISTRACTION, UGLIFICATION, AND DERISION!\""
      },
