      "id": "book10-the-lobster-dance",
      "name": "THE LOBSTER DANCE",
      "level": 1,
      "category": "booklet",
      "sort_order": 10,
      "sections": {
        "Page 1": "\"LET ME SHOW YOU THE LOBSTER DANCE!\"\nSAID THE MOCK TURTLE.\nTHEY ALL DANCED ON THE BEACH.\n\"WILL YOU WALK A LITTLE FASTER?\"\nSANG THE MOCK TURTLE.",
        "Page 2": "THE MOCK TURTLE SANG A SONG:\n\"BEAUTIFUL SOUP, SO RICH AND GREEN,\nWAITING IN A HOT TUREEN!\"\nHE LOVED SOUP VERY MUCH.",
        "Page 3": "THEN SOMEONE SHOUTED:\n\"THE TRIAL IS STARTING!\"\nTHE GRYPHON GRABBED ALICE'S HAND.\n\"COME ON!\" HE SAID. \"LET US GO!\""
      },
